hw3: Scene in 3D

John Osborne
CSCI4229/5229 Fall 2019

Draw a scene in 3D with repeated generics

Key bindings
  m          Toggle between perspective and orthogonal
  +/-        Changes field of view for perspective
  a          Toggle axes
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit
